Here is everything about the Style ;D










Below is the full copy paste code 
--------------------------------------------

.color-holder {
    width: 400px;     // Here you can set the width of the Box
    height: 400px;    //  Here you can set the height of the box
    background-color: yellow;   // here you can set the background-color
    margin-top: 20px;   // Here you can set how much space you want on top of the box
    margin-bottom: 25px;    // Here you can set how much space you want on the bottom of the box
    border: 9px dotted pink //    Here you can set the border color / style 
  }
.toggle-color {
  background-color: blue;   // Here you can select what color the button should toggle on the box
}

